'''Kingston Escarpment & Iford Hill''' is a 64.4 hectare (159.1 acre) biological [[Site of Special Scientific Interest]] in [[East Sussex]], [[England]]. The site was [[SSSI notification|notified]] in 1986 under the [[Wildlife and Countryside Act 1981]]. 

